+-------------------------------------------------------------+
| unixODBC                                                    |
| Driver Config for MySQL ODBC driver                         |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+

Use this Driver Config when using the MySQL
ODBC Driver.

It allows ODBCConfig to prompt the user for Data Source
options.

ODBCConfig will read the "Setup" entry in
/etc/odbcinst.ini to determine the name of the config
lib to use.

